    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Andean refers to the cultures, styles, and expressions rooted in the Indigenous cultural heritage of the Andes, the continental mountain range of South America that transcends political boundaries. It encompasses both the native peoples of the pre-Hispanic era and the contemporary inhabitants of the region.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
